Baseline details for specific subjects

Source: R/sdtm_class.R
subject_info.sdtm.Rd

Baseline details for specific subjects

Usage

# S3 method for class 'sdtm'
subject_info(obj, id)

Arguments

obj

The object, either an SDTM or NIF object.

id

The ID or USUBJID as numeric or character.

Examples

subject_info(examplinib_fe, subjects(examplinib_fe)[1, "USUBJID"])
#>          [,1]             
#> SITEID   102              
#> SUBJID   1020001          
#> ACTARM   Fed - Fasted     
#> ACTARMCD BA               
#> RFICDTC  2000-12-21T10:29 
#> RFSTDTC  2000-12-26T10:29 
#> RFXSTDTC 2000-12-26T10:29 
#> STUDYID  2023000400       
#> USUBJID  20230004001020001
#> SEX      M                
#> AGE      22               
#> AGEU     YEARS            
#> COUNTRY  DEU              
#> DOMAIN   DM               
#> ARM      Fed - Fasted     
#> ARMCD    BA               
#> RACE     WHITE            
#> ETHNIC                    
#> RFENDTC  2001-01-08T10:29
